1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:05,040
Bitcoin dropped four percent after the Federal Reserve held interest rates steady.

2
00:00:05,490 --> 00:00:11,036
Markets expected a more hawkish tone, but the Fed kept rates unchanged for now.

3
00:00:11,487 --> 00:00:16,164
Ethereum followed Bitcoin lower, falling about three percent on the day.

4
00:00:16,614 --> 00:00:21,713
Analysts say crypto remains highly sensitive to Federal Reserve policy.

5
00:00:22,163 --> 00:00:28,227
Major altcoins also slid, with total crypto market cap down roughly two percent.

